683
00:32:19.720 --> 00:32:20.798
Oh.

684
00:32:21.565 --> 00:32:23.391
Well. I mean. if you think it's time.

685
00:32:23.392 --> 00:32:26.594
I hate the idea of
leaving you here alone

686
00:32:26.595 --> 00:32:29.135
