with Warren Beatty in '67.
she's an authority on every...

701
00:33:02.303 --> 00:33:04.678
No. no. no. stop. stop.
stop. What... Okay.

702
00:33:04.679 --> 00:33:06.679
What. what do you mean Dad has dementia?

703
00:33:07.649 --> 00:33:10.246
